  "rationale": "Lean 6-section scroll. Hero adapts card-over-portrait-statement on the only inverse surface, keeping the sanctioned panel-on-media (space-between) and carrying the single accent on its display statement. About reuses the anchored statement, adding a low-opacity ABOUT ghost word for brand flavor. Gallery reuses the full-bleed counter-band. Heritage adapts tucked-headline-panorama to primary (hero stays the sole inverse), keeping the z:back straddle tuck with medium occlusion + endsVisible, sanctioned. Visit is a novel split cta pairing info + map + underline newsletter; footer closes with slash-nav and socials. Mission and curator folded to stay under the 6-section ceiling."
